[b][size="4"]Personal Info[/size][/b]

[b]First name[/b]
<%= @applicant.name %>

[b]Age[/b]
<%= @applicant.age %>

[b]Time zone[/b]
<%= @applicant.time_zone %>

[b]Play times[/b]
<%- %w(sunday monday tuesday wednesday thursday friday saturday).each do |day| -%>
<%= @applicant.attributes["start_#{day}"].strftime("%I:%M %p") %> until <%= @applicant.attributes["end_#{day}"].strftime("%I:%M %p") %> CST <%= day.titlecase %>
<%- end -%>

[b]List any current Juggernaut members you know and how you know them[/b]
<%= @applicant.known_members %>

[b]List any current or near future commitments you have that might affect your raid attendance[/b]
<%= @applicant.future_commitments %>

[b]Why do you want to join Juggernaut?[/b]
<%= @applicant.reasons_for_joining %>

[b][size="4"]Character Information[/size][/b]

[b]Current server[/b]
<%= @applicant.server.name %>

[b]Current name[/b]
<%= @applicant.character_name %>

[b]Class[/b]
<%= @applicant.character_class %>

[b]Current race[/b]
<%= @applicant.character_race %>

[b]Armory link[/b]
[url="<%= @applicant.armory_link %>"]<%= @applicant.armory_link %>[/url]

[b]Describe, in detail, your entire guild history across all of your characters, and your reasons for leaving each guild[/b]
<%= @applicant.previous_guilds %>

[b]Describe your previous PvE experience[/b]
<%= @applicant.pve_experience %>

[b]Describe your previous PvP experience[/b]
<%= @applicant.pvp_experience %>

[b]Provide a link to a screenshot of your interface during a raid[/b]
<%- if @applicant.screenshot_link.present? -%>
[img]<%= @applicant.screenshot_link %>[/img]
<%- end -%>

[b][size="4"]System Information[/size][/b]

[b]What type of connection do you normally play on?[/b]
<%= @applicant.connection_type %>

[b]Do you have a microphone?[/b]
<%= @applicant.has_microphone? ? 'Yes' : 'No' %>

[b]Do you have Ventrilo installed on your computer?[/b]
<%= @applicant.has_ventrilo? ? 'Yes' : 'No' %>

[b]Do you talk on Ventrilo?[/b]
<%= @applicant.uses_ventrilo? ? 'Yes' : 'No' %>

[b][size="4"]Additional Comments[/size][/b]

<%= @applicant.comments %>